item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - MMC (Mickey Mouse Club) - MMC: The Album [1993]
item.description:
​

MMC (also referred to as MMC: The Album) is an album recorded by several members of the cast of The All-New Mickey Mouse Club (1989-1994). It was released on September 13, 1993 by Walt Disney Records.

While there were no official single releases, several tracks appeared in various media, including the 1993 romantic comedy, My Boyfriend's Back.

Performers JC Chasez and Rhona Bennett would go on to have successful music careers as members of *NSYNC and En Vogue, respectively, while Tony Lucca and Jennifer McGill would have varying degrees of success as solo artists.

1. Flava (lead vocals: Tony Lucca)
2. Real Talk (lead vocals: Rhona Bennett)
3. I Want Your Love (lead vocals: Nita Booth)
4. Cool Love (lead vocals: Tony Lucca)
5. Goodbye Doesn't Mean I'm Gone (lead vocals: Rhona Bennett)
6. Gimme Back My Groove (lead vocals: Nita Booth)
7. Step to the Rhythm (lead vocals: Dale Godboldo)
8. I Saw Her First (lead vocals: JC Chasez)
9. Time With You (lead vocals: Nita Booth)
10. Hanging On For Dear Life (lead vocals: Jennifer McGill)
11. Merry-Go-Round (lead vocals: Matt Morris)
12. Let's Get Together (lead vocals: JC Chasez)
